=TITLE save_set1
=TITLE Saving Puzzle Settings
=INCLUDE Overview Settings rest_set1
=INCLUDE Overview Settings ok_but
=INCLUDE Overview Settings can_but
=KEYWORD Saving Setting
 Choose the Save Settings menu item in the Customize
 menu to permanently save changes that you have made to
 the Puzzle.

3  rest_set1
=TITLE rest_set1
=TITLE Restoring Puzzle Settings
=INCLUDE Overview Settings save_set1
=INCLUDE Overview Settings ok_but
=INCLUDE Overview Settings can_but
=KEYWORD Restoring Setting
 Choose the Use System Defaults menu item in the
 Customize menu to restore the DECwindows default
 settings for the Puzzle.

 Any previous changes you made to the Puzzle will no
 longer take effect.

