2  Popup_menu
=TITLE Popup_menu
=TITLE Accessing the Puzzle Pop-Up Menu
=INCLUDE Overview Settings
=INCLUDE Overview New_Game
=INCLUDE Overview Exiting
=INCLUDE Overview Menus
=KEYWORD Starting Menus Customizing Quitting
 Puzzle contains a pop-up menu that allows you to access
 some of the Puzzle menu items more quickly.

 To do this, press and hold mouse button 3 (MB3)
 anywhere in the puzzle (but not in the menu or title
 bars). A pop-up menu is displayed. Choose New Game,
 Settings, or Quit and release MB3.

